cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image classification and proposes a new convolutional neural network architecture for indoor scene classification. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper introduces a new learnable feature descriptor and proposes a methodology for efficient training of the network model. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing a robust feature representation for automatic indoor scene categorization. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with image classification and feature representation, which are relevant to information retrieval tasks. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image classification and proposes a new feature descriptor for indoor scene classification, which is relevant to multimedia applications.
